project.title: Programming Historian Sample Project
project.description:
Sample project for Programming Historian lesson proposal, annotating a Radiolab podcast called "Driverless Dilemma." This podcast was originally introduced in the Fall '23 and Spring '24 versions of Rhetoric 306 at UT Austin. 
Link to Sam's 306 syllabus: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1CFEmfe1dt5asQ4L1zxQ0Qqhya99gYIfG/edit
